OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close
OL,4,Ctemporarily due to safety concerns
OL,6,FThe Menai Suspension Bridge will close
OL,7,Ftemporarily due to safety concerns,
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government has announced.
OL,10,FThe closure will come into force from
OL,11,F2pm on Saturday, 4 October, following
OL,12,Fenforcement challenges highlighted by
OL,13,FUK Highways A55.
OL,15,FDespite efforts to keep the bridge
OL,16,Fopen to cars and motorcyclists, a
OL,17,Frecent investigation revealed that
OL,18,Fbolts on beams under the bridge need
OL,19,Fto be replaced.
