OL,6,FThis discovery, along with feedback
OL,7,Ffrom UK Highways A55 regarding
OL,8,Fdifficulties in enforcing
OL,9,Frestrictions, led to the decision to
OL,10,Fimplement a full closure.
OL,12,FEmergency service vehicle arrangements
OL,13,Fhave been put in place in the event
OL,14,Fthat high winds affect the nearby
OL,15,FBritannia Bridge.
