OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close
OL,4,Ctemporarily due to safety concerns
OL,6,FCabinet Secretary for Transport and
OL,7,FNorth Wales, Ken Skates, said:
OL,8,F"Firstly, I want to apologise to local
OL,9,Fpeople. I am deeply sorry for the
OL,10,Fongoing disruption that you are facing
OL,11,Fas work continues to remediate the
OL,12,Fbridge.
