OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close
OL,4,Ctemporarily due to safety concerns
OL,6,F"We have explored every option to keep
OL,7,Fthe bridge open safely but following
OL,8,Fthis latest feedback on enforcement
OL,9,Ffrom UK Highways A55, who are
OL,10,Fresponsible for the maintenance of the
OL,11,Fbridge, our hand has been forced to
OL,12,Fintroduce a full closure. I'd like to
OL,13,Fthank the police for their support
OL,14,Fover the past 24 hours."
OL,16,FHe added: "I am incredibly frustrated
OL,17,Fat this latest development, and I can
OL,18,Fassure you that my officials and I are
OL,19,Fpressing UK Highways A55 for an early
OL,20,Fresolution to this issue.
