OL,3,CMenai Suspension Bridge to close
OL,4,Ctemporarily due to safety concerns
OL,6,F"However, despite all our frustrations
OL,7,Fwe must listen to the advice from
OL,8,Fengineers to ensure the safety of
OL,9,Feveryone."
OL,11,F"The bridge closure will remain in
OL,12,Fplace until further investigations are
OL,13,Fcompleted in the coming days and UK
OL,14,FHighways A55 have provided us with a
OL,15,Fsafe enforcement strategy, to reopen
OL,16,Fthe bridge and move forward with phase
OL,17,Ftwo works.
OL,19,F"During this time, we will continue to
OL,20,Fkeep you updated and I thank you once
OL,21,Fagain for your patience."
